@runId = aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa

### GET /reconciliations/{runId}/results - All results (replace runId)
GET http://localhost:8080/reconciliations/{{runId}}/results

### GET /reconciliations/{runId}/results - With pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/reconciliations/{{runId}}/results?page=0&size=50

### GET /reconciliations/{runId}/results - Filter by single category
GET http://localhost:8080/reconciliations/{{runId}}/results?category=MISMATCHED

### GET /reconciliations/{runId}/results - Filter by multiple categories
GET http://localhost:8080/reconciliations/{{runId}}/results?category=MISMATCHED&category=UNRECONCILED_PROCESSOR&category=UNRECONCILED_INTERNAL

### GET /reconciliations/{runId}/results - Size exceeds maximum (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/reconciliations/{{runId}}/results?size=201

### GET /reconciliations/{runId}/results - Run not found (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/reconciliations/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/results